Generic DNS server to dynamically distribute load among a given set of resources

GOALS
 * add/remove/change zones on the fly
 * add/remove/change resources on the fly
 * add/remove/change nodes on the fly
 * change policy for how nodes for a given resource are allocated on the fly
 * discover peer balancers
 * maintain persistent connections to peer balancers
 * distribute/receive changes to zones/resources/nodes among peers

-- Dependencies --
dnsbalance
 * dnode
 * winston
 * optimist
 * hashish
 * chainsaw

node-dns
 * bufferjs
 * https://github.com/tjfontaine/node-struct/tarball/master
 * ipaddr.js
